oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Tellico farm
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: A farm in the forest at Tellico. A house, with porch and chimney, and wooden barn are situated in a cleared area of land. A crop appears to be growing in one of the fields. Several fences are visible.
